parameters.content:
# 🛠️ Setup Guide  
**Author:** [Dhruv](https://www.youtube.com/@aiwithdhruv)

Follow the steps below to get this workflow up and running:

---

### ✅ Step 1: Add Your [VAPI](https://vapi.ai/) API Key  
- Grab your API key from VAPI  
- In n8n, create a **Generic Credential** using **Bearer Auth**  
- Paste your VAPI API key into the **two HTTP Request** nodes that require VAPI

---

### ✅ Step 2: Add the System Prompt to Your VAPI Assistant  
- Open your VAPI Assistant settings  
- Copy/paste the system prompt from this doc:  
  👉 **System Prompt (Copy Link):** [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/u/1/d/1IQV-azxjKCdrxhqOespddFFKEJY8CXjObINN4xFn3es/copy)

---

### ✅ Step 3: Connect a Phone Number in VAPI  
- Connect (or purchase) a phone number inside VAPI  
- In the **Call Lead** HTTP Request node, make sure you set:  
  - **Your Assistant ID**  
  - **Your Phone Number ID**

---

### ✅ Step 4: Connect the Google Sheet Template  
- Make a copy of the template here:  
  👉 **Google Sheet Template (Copy Link):** [Google Sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1NEEmrQhRC0cGLyYKa0qTr5e72Iub38_tZFs4l37PwTk/copy)  
- Connect your Google credentials in n8n  
- Point the workflow to **your copied sheet** (not the original template)

---

### 💡 Final Check  
Before running, confirm:
- VAPI key is present in both required HTTP Request nodes  
- Assistant ID + Phone Number ID are correctly set in **Call Lead**  
- Google Sheet connection points to your copied template
